{"tid":2076920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立法會通過終止審議空置稅","createTime":"2020-06-24T02:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T15:53:22.000Z","uid":228995,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"785f96b60f3c047ee5eb6b11f8d8060af502203a","tid":2076920,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:01:47.000Z","msg":"//【Now新聞台】立法會通過終止審議空置稅。<br />\n<br />\n立法會繼續審議2019年差餉修訂條例草案，討論政府向空置的一手私人住宅單位徵收額外差餉，有多名議員批評政策未能對症下藥，又質疑在今屆立法會會期內無足夠時間完成審議，最終由委員會主席林健鋒提出終止委員會工作，獲在席議員一致通過，即在下屆會期前，政府不能提出向一手樓徵收空置稅。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=395523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395523&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=43089d6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395523&h=8e4e0ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=395523</a><br />\n<br />\n國家面前，立空置稅簡直微不足道。"},{"pid":"adb0f085e465719ccd7014a3c9db61f6bf470fae","tid":2076920,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"尋日垃圾徵費係咪都收咗皮"},{"pid":"adabbd5aa977e7b3949686a18f9e1d731d2d4540","tid":2076920,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"在下屆會期前，政府不能提出向一手樓徵收空置稅<br />\n<br />\n好快下屆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9112073efc8584aeff5d3cff425f30f8ff0d33ec","tid":2076920,"uid":179775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依個時候點會得罪有錢佬呀"},{"pid":"18194afd088943a7f2b683b4990e7da824e9e3d0","tid":2076920,"uid":261913,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:45:45.000Z","msg":"方便中聯辦掃樓？<img src=\"/assets/face